Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}翻译 童话 明撒 永叔 天井 校译 茶 时间 岚 后期 小克 压制 追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没想到是发动攻击的剑断掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说 我造的剑比想象中还要弱的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话说在前面 只要有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能轻易斩断你那把剑的武器 几把我都造的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 那就一定拜托你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造出一把轻易斩断我的剑的武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既…既然你这么说 我就奉陪到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 从收集金属材料开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人就够了 你碍手碍脚的我也很为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我啊 我好歹也是个优秀的锻造师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 材料的地址是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在55层西边的山里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有以吃水晶为生的巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那龙的体内好像就积蓄着稀少金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,55层啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要获得金属的话 没有锻造师可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样你也打算一个人去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好躲在角落里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剑锻造好之前 总之 请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多关照了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一来就直叫姓名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹贝特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.17,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\be2\blur3\pos(544,502)}第55层·西边的山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有多余的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道55层是冰雪地带啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你身体的锻炼方式可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每句话都惹人生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会和这样的男人单独出门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真是怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 莉兹贝特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢 话说回来 反正我对直接叫你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也直接叫莉兹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 我知道了 莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太得意！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好转移水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 从这里开始我一个人上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹 如果巨龙出现了 你就躲在那边的水晶后面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要现身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 我又不是什么新手 一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去躲在那边的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冻攻击 快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那样细的武器就…到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 赶快解决掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 还不可以出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是已经要完了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹 抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先喝下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 谢谢你 救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谢谢还早了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？转移不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移 林达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用转移水晶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说有其他出去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有没有那种方法谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是掉下来的人 100%会死的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这也有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 稍微给点力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沿着墙壁跑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是白痴 试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果助跑距离还能长点话 应该就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得怪怪的 一点真实感都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在初次来的地方和初次见到的人 并排着睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还沿着墙壁跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很奇怪的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 桐人 问你点事行么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候 要救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看着某个人死的话 还不如一起死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是和莉兹这样样的女孩的话 就更不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋呢 这样的人 找不出第二个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…握紧我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我和桐人都是假想世界的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}水晶石英铸块(crystallite ingot)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个难道是……？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我们来寻找的金属吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白龙吞下水晶 在腹中精制而成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个凹坑不是陷阱 而是白龙的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个铸块是白龙的排泄物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是粪便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 目标达成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你刚才说这里是白龙的巢穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白龙应该是夜行性动物吧 差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 干…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹 抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:30.23,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,499)\fad(300,200)\be2}2024年6月25日     第48层 林达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单手剑就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人手心的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冶炼出令他满意的剑后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对他表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫逐暗者(dark repulser)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字我第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还没登陆到情报商店名册上的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎……怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是把好剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉倾注了灵魂一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下委托完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑的铸造费我会付的 多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 钱的话我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想成为桐人专属的铁匠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从野外回来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里 我帮你保养装备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天如此 从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹 害我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚斯娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法传递信息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没法追踪地图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚到底去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微被困在了洞穴里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 和这个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…亚丝娜 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是呢 两天不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说声的话 我就陪你一起过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩 难道是熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们两个都是攻略组的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他想要一把强力的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就介绍了莉兹的店给他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没对我的好朋友做什么奇怪的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支支吾吾的地方好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是从鬼门关回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹体谅一下我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才和你说那么多次 不要单独行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 有没有对莉兹说了什么很失礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一下子就把我的店最好的剑给折断了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 又不用亚丝娜道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 他虽然怪了点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是坏人 我会支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以加油啊 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我和人约好去采购了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 店怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你们俩看店啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹贝特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 你现在跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明再等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能回到平常那个精神百倍莉兹贝特了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那眺望整个城镇 才找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一样乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只是被不习惯的冒险吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我说过的 全都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想向莉兹道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都认为与其一个人幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如死了更好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 掉进洞穴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起活下来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我了解到 无论是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别人 都是为了活下去而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也一直在寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界里的存在着的 真实的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 那个就是桐人的手传来的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的那些话 也说给亚丝娜听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这股温暖还会残留一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 将这个世界终结掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那个时候 我都会努力下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证 一定会通关的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要修理武器和防具的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎随时光临啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多多关照 莉兹贝特武器店
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くに聞こえた　鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:29.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远处传来的钟声 传达着淡淡的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:34.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今度は高く　駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:41.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定能达到更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ繰り返す現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:47.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是在无限反复着的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:53.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}还是那些如同繁星般多的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目指すべき明日を見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:58.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在找到前进方向的我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}この想いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:04.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}全都战胜不了这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}目の前に開かれた果てない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:11.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}在眼前无限延伸的这没有尽头的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}たとえ仮想でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:15.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}即使是梦也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}迷い続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}就算会一直迷路下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}夢の奥で強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:22.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}只要能在这梦中变强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}ずっと　ずっと　響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}愿此思念 永远响彻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}そっと　そっと　光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:34.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}愿此思念 永远闪耀
